Female genitalia (
Fig. 25 a
). Gonocoxites 8 slighlty convex, with a submarginal depression along the sutural and posterior margins. Pars intermedialis with parallel lateral margins; diameter of capsula seminalis four times the diameter of pars intermedialis. Processes of capsula seminalis with different lengths: the longer process five times the length of pars intermedialis and twice the length of the shorter. Longer process of the capsula seminalis twisted. Distribution. Brazil : Minas Gerais, Rio de Janeiro, São Paulo, Paraná, Santa Catarina and Rio Grande do Sul.
